{"id": "mem_rel_001", "text": "在AI conference偶遇Zhang Wei，听了他关于RLHF挑战的演讲。会后聊了10分钟，说'你的落地方向和我想的不一样，我想的是用RLHF做儿童教育内容过滤，不是成人'。交换了微信", "category": "social_connection", "agent_id": "principal", "importance": 0.7, "source": "conference社交记录", "metadata": "{\"person\": \"Zhang_Wei\", \"context\": \"conference\", \"first_impression\": \"学术派+落地意识强\", \"topic\": \"RLHF_content_moderation\"}", "created_at": 1705766400000}
{"id": "mem_rel_002", "text": "Zhang Wei发了篇新论文在ArXiv，题目是'Calibrating RLHF for Age-Appropriate Content in Educational LLMs'。看了觉得有意思——他真的往儿童教育走了，但我的需求其实是'防止LLM生成儿童不宜内容'，方向反了", "category": "social_connection", "agent_id": "principal", "importance": 0.7, "source": "学术跟踪记录", "metadata": "{\"person\": \"Zhang_Wei\", \"paper\": \"arXiv_2024_0512\", \"paper_topic\": \"children_education_RLHF\", \"my_use_case_divergence\": true}", "created_at": 1715136000000}
{"id": "mem_rel_003", "text": "和Zhang Wei微信聊了一次。他说他正在找教育场景的RLHF数据合作，说'你们有儿童对话数据吗'。我说'我们有过滤掉成人内容的对话数据，但不是标注过的RLHF数据，但可以介绍我认识的张教授'", "category": "social_connection", "agent_id": "principal", "importance": 0.75, "source": "用户对话", "metadata": "{\"person\": \"Zhang_Wei\", \"interaction_type\": \"wechat_call\", \"opportunity\": \"RLHF_data_collaboration\", \"my_contribution\": \"referral_to_prof_zhang\"}", "created_at": 1720012800000}
{"id": "mem_rel_004", "text": "Zhang Wei发消息说论文中了顶会，说'谢谢当时你介绍的张教授，数据合作最后成了'。问我要不要联名署名作为数据贡献者。想了想拒绝了，说'我给你做了个引子，但核心研究是你做的，联名会稀释你的贡献'", "category": "social_connection", "agent_id": "principal", "importance": 0.8, "source": "用户对话", "metadata": "{\"person\": \"Zhang_Wei\", \"outcome\": \"paper_accepted_top_conf\", \"my_role\": \"data_provider_referral\", \"my_decision\": \"decline_coauthor\", \"reason\": \"principal_contribution_principle\"}", "created_at": 1736899200000}
